%section.plugin-list
  %h2 About Gauge plugins
  %p.text-block Gauge has a very plugin supportive architecture. Gauge core is written in Golang, and it has a rich of plugins. Everything is Gauge is a plugin. Language runners, IDEs are also plugins. You can read more about how to use Gauge plugins here.
  %p.text-block You can also write a new plugin using the plugin API. More on this here.

